&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;We use to raid buff wtih Symbols, Ward and Druid Oak. That gave you more hit points and ac then just plain virtue...&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Now When I buff with the new Direwood 2&amp;nbsp; / Symbol 2 and Ward&amp;nbsp; I get 100hp and 50ac less then just buffing with Tencity.&amp;nbsp; I am trying to understand if there is any advantage now to buffing with them 3 anymore. Was this an SOE oversight?&amp;nbsp; Or is there still some reason to use them 3 buffs together?&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
