      <description>Thought I'd post this as a heads up. With TSS, they're opening up the OoW spells to be researchable. Depending on how it's done, the spell Placate might become much easier to obtain after this goes in since Placate is likely to be treated as a level 67 spell (since that's when enchanters get it). If you've just gotten your first glowing rune (or will get one soon), you might want to consider holding off till after TSS and see if you can get placate via easier means before doing your turn in.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
