      <title>Something odd I noticed</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=clericbalance&amp;message.id=11451#M11451</link>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;I started playing a cleric on the Progression server to try it out and I noticed something odd.&lt;br&gt;The spell rebalancing did improve the efficiency of heals (for all classes) and it made them available to some classes including clerics at earlier levels then before. What also happened was the sliding scale of amount healed being dependant on level. This is where it gets interesting.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Take the first two cleric heals, &lt;a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=200&amp;amp;source=Live" target="_blank"&gt;Minor Healing&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=17&amp;amp;source=Live" target="_blank"&gt;Light Healing&lt;/a&gt;. Unfortunately Lucy doesn't give an easily understandable description of the range of hp heal depending on the level for Light Healing.&lt;br&gt;At level 6, minor gives a 2:1 ratio for amount healed to mana used. Light (healing about 53 hp) gives only about 1.9:1 at this level. It takes until about level 8 or 9 to match the efficiency of Minor Healing. It is at level 9 that Druids and shaman get this heal. All 3 priests have the same level of efficiency from level 1-9 and I would assume beyond until Superior Healing and level 37.&lt;br&gt;Yes clerics will have a higher output of hphealed/second but does that matter at those levels? So until level 37 all 3 priests are as efficient healers as each other. Was this always the way? Casting our newest heals was less efficient then using those the spell circle below?&lt;br&gt;It seems odd to me, not at all like I remember it.&lt;br&gt;Of course with all that said clerics have a 5% bonus to the amount healed by heals.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;What I'm getting at is that I think the healing spell changes reduced some of the healing advantage clerics once had at lower levels. Actually just looking at on old spell list I found clerics heals were more efficient as soon as a new spell circle (containing a heal) was reached.&lt;br&gt;At lower levels clerics have become more efficient healers but we have definitely lost some of our healing advantage.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
